{"tid":656231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［正視聽］ 母語係一個偽命題","createTime":"2018-05-07T05:05:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-08T15:53:27.000Z","uid":15831,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a2257e2b86aaba27645f3f8494d1800861404c24","tid":656231,"uid":15831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T05:05:49.000Z","msg":"就好似 「台獨」 一樣<br />\n當你講 「支持台獨」 -  下意識就首先承認左台灣係「需要」獨立，而無視左台灣本來就已經係一個獨立國家既事實<br />\n<br />\n討論 「母語」- 有人用普通話 vs 廣東話 既優劣嚟證明香港人應該講廣東話作為母語， 因為廣東話優雅，blablabla <br />\n<br />\n而事實上 「母語」性質上係無討論空間<br />\n等如你問我係 男 / 女 一樣， 何需討論 比較<br />\n<br />\n就算廣東話差過非洲土著話都好<br />\n佢作為香港人出世第一種聽/用既語言係完全無質疑既理由<br />\n<br />\n要反駁呢種 「香港人母語係咩」既白痴問題<br />\n第一點先要知道呢個問題既根本並唔係 「廣東話屬唔屬於母語」 ， 或者廣東話 vs 普通話優劣<br />\n就咁答一句： 「廣東話」 就夠，任何添加既理由都多餘"},{"pid":"cf4230c5b32ad371257bc12c4cc05f8a97aee788","tid":656231,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T09:32:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f097abd179871d228d191f42ceb3112863c70cc0","tid":656231,"uid":176366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T09:37:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9872f3d2db9bb8b2a3f02b2dfa2f43b4a8c7c658","tid":656231,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T10:49:37.000Z","msg":"d皇漢死都要將粵語打為正統漢語，後果就係，當對方拿出粵語受百越影響既證據既時候就會定左係度，唔識反駁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbfd270638bfff0559099a54dc94544dcc400882","tid":656231,"uid":59465,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T10:51:10.000Z","msg":"偽命題=支那用詞<br />\n收皮啦"},{"pid":"5512e69b66c0d02bbf8c956ffddfa480ad73afe5","tid":656231,"uid":15831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbfd270638bfff0559099a54dc94544dcc400882","tid":656231,"uid":59465,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T10:51:10.000Z","msg":"偽命題=支那用詞<br />\n收皮啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:26:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://dic.nicovideo.jp/a/%E5%91%BD%E9%A1%8C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdic.nicovideo.jp%2Fa%2F%25E5%2591%25BD%25E9%25A1%258C&d=9wiCCIPEbKP8v7XMGyRO%2By7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=c624c415\" target=\"_blank\">http://dic.nicovideo.jp/a/%E5%91%BD%E9%A1%8C</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%91%BD%E9%A1%8C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fja.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%2591%25BD%25E9%25A1%258C&d=9wiCCIPEbKP8v7XMGyRO%2By7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=e17cc84d\" target=\"_blank\">https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%91%BD%E9%A1%8C</a><br />\n<br />\n有啲字唔係支那用過就係變左支那用詞"},{"pid":"583e0313bcd9f13f07590aeddd54b556fd282614","tid":656231,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:28:07.000Z","msg":"食屎啦屌你老母 你咁講即係叫人唔好重視呢個問題 無人重視 港共就會更加不遺餘力咁做落去"},{"pid":"4fa5a246168ffcdf030ba1771e0bc8bbf55bfbee","tid":656231,"uid":78336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T13:50:18.000Z","msg":"偽命題你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n台獨係講緊脫離中華民國 唔係脫離中共 <br />\n脫離左就唔再處於內戰狀態<br />\n意思係唔再同共匪爭大陸 共匪唔該咪撚搞我<br />\n<br />\n第二就係 廣東話母語同優劣之分既混淆呢個不嬲都係你想像既討論<br />\n優劣係回應緊推普 而唔係母語論<br />\n母語論係呢兩日先彈出黎既謬誤"},{"pid":"ba3f4d8599af23872a3a4a44e6cf1ca091cd90b4","tid":656231,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T15:53:27.000Z","msg":"同 共產黨最開心 本質上有咩分別？"}]}